headline: Federal Realty Investment Trust Reports First Quarter 2025 Results
summary: Federal Realty Investment Trust (NYSE:FRT) today reported its results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2025. For the three months ended March 31, 2025 and 2024, net income available for common shareholders was $0.72 per diluted share and $0.66 per diluted share, respectively. Operating income for the same periods was $108.1 million and $100.2 million, respectively.
